results.title: Promises
results.description: Kingpin tries to get Ben under his thumb by using his wife's desire for a new house to turn Urich dirty; Ben has to decide how best to be a good reporter, a good husband and a good man.

results.title: Bitsy's Revenge
results.description: DD is on the trail of some stolen missiles, and they lead him to a cruise ship and a traveling magician who doesn't know the gun she stole off of the guard she killed at the heist doesn't work.

results.title: Betrayal
results.description: Tarkington Brown, who works for the mayor, finds that he only has a few weeks to live, so he recruits some cops to form a criminal killing murder squad as his way of making a final contribution before he dies; While she is drunk at a party, Heather tells Tark that Matt is DD, and Tarkington sends his squad to take down the Man Without Fear.

results.title: Enemies
results.description: Bullseye is taken by Lord Dark Wind (the inventor of the adamantium bonding process) onto a ship heading for Japan; Daredevil runs across Wolverine and the two try to track down Bullseye before he leaves the country; Daredevil lets Bullseye go to save the life of Tarkington Brown.

results.title: Journey
results.description: DD is on his way to Japan when he runs across Dark Wind's daughter in chains and frees her; The pair make it to Japan and prepare to get Bullseye away from Yuriko's father before he can fix the crippled villain.

results.title: Touch of a Stranger
results.description: DD and Yuriko get closer to Bullseye and Dark Wind; Dark Wind repairs Bulseye by replacing his broken backbone with adamantium.

results.title: Daughter of a Dark Wind
results.description: A healed Bullseye betrays Dark Wind and makes his way back to the States; Yuriko kills her father to save Daredevil's life.

results.title: The Evil Menace of Electro!
results.description: The Thing and the F.F. hire Matt to look over the new lease on the Baxter Building; Matt goes to inspect the property but, unbeknownst to him, Electro has broken in to steal all of Reed Richard's secrets; Mayhem ensues.

results.title: The Verdict Is Death
results.description: The Owl kidnaps Matt Murdock to be the defense attorney in a mock trial the fowlish fiend has set up for the judge who sent him to prison.

results.title: Redemption
results.description: Daredevil and Bullseye have a final showdown in the ring where Matt's father fought; Story reveals that Jack Murdock wrestled as The Red Devil with a mask similar to DD's.

results.title: DD's Out of Action...But the Widow is back !
The Day The Devil Didn't Dare
results.description: Someone takes a shot at Foggy, and a wounded DD enlists the Widow's aid in trying to find out who is trying to kill his partner.

results.title: Savages
results.description: Micah Synn arrives in New York and doesn't leave for a really long time.

results.title: A Life In the Day
results.description: A young schoolboy does an in depth oral report on Daringdevil which is interrupted by a fight between DD and Turk.

results.title: Trumps
results.description: Dardevil busts up the Trump's gang during a gun theft and captures one of the tormentors who made his childhood a living hell.

results.title: Vengeance of the Victim
results.description: Micah Synn's rich and foppish relative contracts with Crossbow to have the savage killed before he ruins the good Synn name; Debbie throws a huge party and gets a little frisky with Synn; Crossbow and DD show up to spoil the festivities; Tony is drunk for the whole affair.

results.title: The Gael
results.description: Debbie's niece Glorianna arrives from Ireland, and DD has to protect her from The Gael, an I.R.A. hitman gone rogue.

results.title: Every Good and Perfect Gift
results.description: Micah crashes Matt's Christmas party and The Kingpin helps DD keep the savage from abducting Foggy's wife.

results.title: Ultimatum
results.description: Hydra captures the Black Widow and tries to use her to take out Daredevil.

results.title: The Deadliest Night of My Life
results.description: DD is forced to survive the house of death that Death-Stalker's mother has set up as revenge for her son's death.

results.title: Blast From the Past
results.description: DD is still being pursued by the little girl robots activated by the deceased Ms. Sterling and is helped out by one of his childhood tormentors.

results.title: The Trap Is Sprung
results.description: DD has to rescue himself and Judge Lewis from the Owl's giant mechanical owl.

Marvel Masterworks: Daredevil Vol. II - 2nd Edition (1st) (Trade Paperback)

results.title: Survivor
results.description: Micah gets a restraining order against DD; Kingpin catches Micah's men poaching and teaches them a lesson; Micah breaks Crossbow out of prison and uses him to lure DD into a trap; Micah learns that DD and Murdock are one and the same.

results.title: This Hungry God
results.description: Micah captures Becky and Vanessa for a human sacrifice to his god; DD intervenes, but Vanessa is killed; Kingpin reveals that Vanessa was really an actress he hired to keep his wife safe; DD and Kingpin team-up to take down Micah.

results.title: Lies
results.description: Kingpin and DD begin their assault on Synn.

results.title: The Blindness Men Wish For
results.description: DD's war on Synn continues; Foggy finds out how badly Micah mistreated his wife and tries to go to the rescue with DD as backup.

results.title: The Crumbling
results.description: It's an all out chase to get to Michah Synn as Kinpin wants him dead and DD want's to stop the savage before he ends up dead; New York life finally gets to Synn and he drops.

results.title: Prophecy
results.description: DD finishes up a case started by Two-Gun Kid 100 years earlier back in the Wild West.

results.title: The Second Secret
results.description: The Gael puts his face in a pressing machine in prison so he can get out to a hospital and escape; The Gael is after the Old Woman of Beare but DD gets in the way; DD learns that Glori is working for the I.R.A.

results.title: The Sight Stealer
results.description: The Cossack has the power to cause blindness and only New York's blind super hero can stop him and thwart his schemes.

results.title: It Can't Be ! Daredevil is the Jester ?!
All My Laurels You Have Riven Away
results.description: DD masquerades as the Jester so that Powers gets his shot at playing Cyrano to a large audience.

results.title: Behold My Vengeance

results.title: Fear In a Handful of Dust
results.description: A group of Deliverance type baddies capture Glorianna and it's DD and the Widow to the rescue.

results.title: The Price
results.description: The Beyonder gives Matt his sight back, and DD threatens to sue him unless he takes it away again.
